{
  "name": "CustomView",
  "summary": "<p><strong>CustomView</strong> 对象是 <strong>CustomViews</strong> 集合的成员。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>CustomViews</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em>为自定义视图的名称或索引号）可返回 <strong>CustomView</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示名为“example1”自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Show</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿上第一个自定义视图包含打印设置，则显示该自定义视图的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintSettings</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表自定义工作簿视图。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表对象的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个自定义视图的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上所有自定义视图的名称赋值给活动工作表的单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= customViews.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "PrintSettings",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果在自定义视图中包含打印设置，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建活动工作簿中自定义视图及其打印设置和行列设置列表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Print Settings&quot;</span>\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;RowColSettings&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= customViews.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintSettings</span>\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RowColSettings</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作簿上第一个自定义视图是否包含打印设置，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintSettings</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;自定义视图包含打印设置&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;自定义视图未包含打印设置&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RowColSettings",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果自定义视图包括对隐藏行和隐藏列（包括筛选信息）的设置，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建活动工作簿中自定义视图及其打印设置和行列设置列表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Print Settings&quot;</span>\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;RowColSettings&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= customViews.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintSettings</span>\n        worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RowColSettings</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上第二个自定义视图是否包含对隐藏行和隐藏列（包括筛选信息）的设置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RowColSettings</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作簿上第二个自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作簿上第一个自定义视图的名称为“example”，则删除该自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>) {\n        customView.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Show",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>显示自定义视图。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例展示第一张工作簿上第三个自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Show</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作簿上第一个自定义视图的名称为“example”，则展示该自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>) {\n        customView.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Show</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
